{"tid":1382553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奇招罷工！","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:28.000Z","uid":278823,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e548d961d1563564114fa35e63ab17d96e8752e4","tid":1382553,"uid":278823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"在2018年5月，日本岡山縣的巴士司機因福利問題，工會跟巴士公司談不攏，於是所有巴士司機決定罷工，但方法很特別：巴士照揸，但一律不收車資.....結果這招最不擾民，巴士公司也很快跪低！<br />\n<br />\n若香港的公共交通或政府的即時收費也可以是這樣罷工⋯⋯😂😂😂<br />\n<br />\n日本巴士司機罷工新聞連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/186215/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E9%9B%86%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F186215%2F%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%259C%25AD%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2593%25BE%25E6%25B0%2591&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiib7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=4013e23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4/186215/%E8%81%B7%E5%A0%B4%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7-%E9%9B%86%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%93%BE%E6%B0%91</a>"},{"pid":"f989754fc5904b8aebfffb980edd26cc4a8dc4a0","tid":1382553,"uid":105715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"呢個係用嚟對付公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港鐵車長做唔到，巴士更加冇原因咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass